# Environment
# .env and uv.lock are intentionally tracked in THIS repo so the website is
# clone-and-run: .env holds only non-secret config (DB path + table/column
# names), no credentials. Other local env files (.env.local, etc.) stay ignored.
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env

